com.cyc.query.parameters

Interface InferenceParameters

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, InferenceParameterGetter, InferenceParameterSetter<InferenceParameters>

    public interface InferenceParameters
extends Cloneable, InferenceParameterGetter, InferenceParameterSetter<InferenceParameters>

    InferenceParameters is designed to encode the parameters that can be specified for running a Cyc query.
